Title: SHODAN
Author: Shrijit Basak (SBJr)
Type: Automation/Intelligent Assistant/AI
Description: Currently this is just a wrapper over  a collection of scripts which help user to do a certain system wide tasks.
Road Map:
1) Add basic script and interface to interact using command line
2) Allow user to create module to create custom automation
3) Add speach recognition to perform the above said tasks
4) Add smart device alteration tasks
5) Add intelligence so that system can iteself create modules of autmated tasks based on human behaviour
